<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Team Invitation</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .header {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .code {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #0f172a;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Team Invitation</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{recipientEmail}},</p>

            <p>{{inviterName}} has invited you to join the team <strong>{{teamName}}</strong> as a {{role}}.</p>

            {{#if message}}
            <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p><strong>Personal message:</strong></p>
                <p>{{message}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p>Use this invite code during signup:</p>

            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <span class="code">{{inviteCode}}</span>
            </p>

            <p>If you already have an account, sign in and enter the code when prompted. If you don't have an account
                yet, you'll be prompted to create one during the process.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>The Schedule App Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>